    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Any of various tools for grating, powdering or shredding food or other materials handled in a similar way, such as pressed blocks of tobacco or cosmetics.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
